<p><a href="https://gitlab.com/hamadmarri/gamma-text-editor">Gamma (Î“)</a> is a lightweight text editor. It is intended to be an alternative to Gedit or Notepad++. Although the current implementation is tested on Linux with a GNOME desktop environment, it can also run on Linux, Windows and Mac if the dependencies are installed (see the Dependencies section below).</p>

<p>Gamma uses GTK3 (cross-platform GUI toolkit) and PyGObject which is a Python package that provides links to GObject-based libraries, such as GTK, GStreamer, WebKitGTK, GLib, GIO and more.</p>

