<h1 id="dependencies">Dependencies</h1>

<ul>
  <li>GTK+ 3</li>
  <li>GtkSourceview 4 (works for 3.0 but currently need to manually change the version in python files)</li>
  <li>Python 3</li>
  <li>gobject-introspection</li>
</ul>

<p>If you are using Linux with a GNOME desktop, you probably already have these dependencies installed. Iâ€™m not sure if the libraries are installed for other desktops, like KDE, XFCE or MATE. But if you have libgtk-3-0 and python3 installed, then Gamma will probably work.</p>

