<h1 id="installation">Installation</h1>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">git clone https://gitlab.com/hamadmarri/gamma-text-editor
<span class="nb">cd </span>gamma-text-editor 
<span class="nb">chmod</span> +x setup.sh
./setup.sh</code></pre></figure>

<h1 id="use-and-configuration">Use and configuration</h1>

<p>Gamma is a very intuitive text editor, but if you want more information, I suggest you consult the official documentation on their Gitlab at: <a href="https://gitlab.com/hamadmarri/gamma-text-editor">https://gitlab.com/hamadmarri/gamma-text-editor</a></p>

